-------------------------------------------------------------------
     
                         openCRX/Test Core

-------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Create the file build.properties in your home directory with the 
   following content:
   
   opencrx-test.core.datasource=jdbc:postgresql:\/\/localhost\/CRX_2_5?user=postgres&password=manager99&driver=org.postgresql.Driver

3. Open a shell and go to the directory ./test-core. Run ant test.
